1. Decide which business to order from
2. Decide which type of pizza to order
3. Decide what toppings for the pizza
4. Decide delivery or pick up
    4a. delivery
    4b. pick up
5. Decide payment method
    5a. Cash
    5b. Card
6. Delivery instructions
    6a. Customers information
        6a1. Name
        6a2. address
        6a3. phone number
    6b. Gate Code if any
7. Pickup instructions
    7a. Store location
8. Order confirmation
9. Eat your food!
10. New order. Return to step 1.
